descriptionHtml:
Arcadia - A Racemenu Preset
by Spasticon1
Verson 1.0

[color=#000000][size=4][b]Description[/b][/size][/color]
This is a preset based off my Fallout Who fanfic series main character. (Can be found on fanficion.net and AO3)
Her race is Imperial.

[u][b][color=#ff7700]Requires KS Hairdo's![/color][/b][/u]

[b][color=#0000ff][size=4]Install[/size][/color][/b]
Drop contents inside into the data folder.

[color=#ff0000][size=4][b]Uninstall[/b][/size][/color]
Delete the related files.

[size=4][b]Credits[/b][/size]
Bethesda - For Skyrim and Fallout.
The Foundry - For the Fallout Who mod series, the source of insperation for my fanfic series.
NexusMods - For being amazing.
author: Spasticon1
